PROJECTS</strong> ✏️</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create production line projects and sell them on your company's website to earn money or buy other companies projects to speed up your production.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🤝 <strong>PARTNERSHIPS</strong> 🤝</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Partner with the strongest companies and get perks such as the ability to see their progress, a 50% discount on their marketplace projects and get 15% of the prize every time one of your partners wins a world challenge.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >⛲️ <strong>DECORATE</strong> ⛲️</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Decorate your factory with the available decorations including a hologram generator, a vase, neon lights and more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3494930/extras/a2bdda0bd70120524ab98c04365cf4f6.poster.avif?t=1748604773\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3494930/extras/a2bdda0bd70120524ab98c04365cf4f6.webm?t=1748604773\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3494930/extras/a2bdda0bd70120524ab98c04365cf4f6.mp4?t=1748604773\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >⚡ <strong>ENERGY</strong> ⚡</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make sure you always have enough power to run your machines, generate energy through power generators and track consumption through the energy management tool.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3494930/extras/4cb24e94b2554da7f63a730499dfb597.poster.avif?t=1748604773\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3494930/extras/4cb24e94b2554da7f63a730499dfb597.webm?t=1748604773\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3494930/extras/4cb24e94b2554da7f63a730499dfb597.mp4?t=1748604773\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >⚙️ <strong>MANAGE</strong> ⚙️</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Manage your company through your Pocket D86, analyze your factory's progress, purchase the machines and product parts you need, and read blueprints to create your production chains correctly.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3494930/extras/65fbdfa0d9331601159eecea6d9a6674.poster.avif?t=1748604773\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3494930/extras/65fbdfa0d9331601159eecea6d9a6674.webm?t=1748604773\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3494930/extras/65fbdfa0d9331601159eecea6d9a6674.mp4?t=1748604773\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
